title: Howard Stern Presents-The 20th Anniversary Of Alanis Morissette'
description:
Howard Stern Presents:The 20th Anniversary Of Alanis Morissette's 'Jagged Little Pill'  (42:38)


Join Grammy Award-winning host Alanis Morissette as she guides Howard 101 listeners though various live performances from her 1995 "Jagged Little Tour" in addition to her phenomenal acoustic performances on The Howard Stern Show.

Alanis gives an inside look at the album that defined her and the performances that made her an international superstar. Songs from the special include "All I Really Want", "Head Over Feet", "Ironic", "You Oughta Know," and more.

Full Song List

"All I Really Want" (Live in London, 1995)

"Head Over Feet" (The Howard Stern Show, 2004)

"Ironic" (The Howard Stern Show, 2004)

"You Learn" (Live in London, 1995)

"Hand In My Pocket" (The Howard Stern Show, 2008)

"You Oughta Know" (The Howard Stern Show, 2015)

"Perfect" (Live in London, 1995)

"Thank U" (The Howard Stern Show, 2005)
